  "type": "mcq",
  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">Triangle <span class=\"italic\">ABC</span> and triangle <span class=\"italic\">DEF</span> are similar triangles, where <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"line segment A B\"></span></span> and <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"line segment D E \"></span></span> are corresponding sides. If <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"the length of line segment D E equals, 2 times the length of line segment A B \"></span></span> and the perimeter of triangle <span class=\"italic\">ABC</span> is 20, what is the perimeter of triangle <span class=\"italic\">DEF </span>?</p>\n",
